name: Cetus
description: 2021, video, 1920x1920x13s... If you dream of seeing a Cetus, do not go to the beach, for this is a warning. If you dream of being eaten, you will have a run of bad luck. If you dream that you are in a Cetus, this is a sign that you will have many good friends. If it is sleeping, the season will be good, but if it is awake, it is time to wake up.
